---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Resume — Konstantin Peselev"
  description="Resume of Konstantin Peselev: Senior Product Manager with 10+ years in B2B SaaS."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-24">
    <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-10 gap-6 flex-wrap">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold text-accent-700 mb-3">Resume</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
          Konstantin Peselev
        </h1>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/konstantin-peselev-resume.pdf"
        class="bg-accent-700 hover:bg-accent-900 text-white font-medium px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Download PDF
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="resume-content">
      <h2>Experience</h2>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-company">Totango · 2022 – 2025</p>
        <p class="resume-role">Senior Product Manager</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Owned product strategy for a $40M ARR Customer Success platform serving 350+ B2B customers including SAP, GitHub, and Dynatrace. Led three engineering squads across Growth, Data Governance, and AI roadmap.</li>
          <li>Owned Growth strategy for SMB segment: shipped intent-driven onboarding, self-learning tools, new monetization model, and self-serve subscription management. Doubled segment revenue; lifted activation rate 2× within four weeks of release.</li>
          <li>Built the AI Account Executive Summary to synthesize personalized insights from large unstructured datasets. Secured adoption by 9 of the top 10 largest enterprise customers.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-company">MyDealerOnline · 2018 – 2022</p>
        <p class="resume-role">Senior Product Manager</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Joined 5-person pre-seed company; grew headcount past 30, ARR past $1M, closed institutional VC round.</li>
          <li>Sourced and integrated five enterprise data partnerships (Black Book, Hyundai Capital, others); built MVP that anchored next funding round and nearly doubled revenue in 12 months.</li>
          <li>Solved attribution by leveraging ML/AI to correlate online engagement with offline sales; productized as automated ROI report that became primary proof-of-value for enterprise deals and renewals.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-company">LTV Europe · 2013 – 2018</p>
        <p class="resume-role">Co-Founder and Managing Director</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Co-founded OEM CCTV distributor for EMEA; raised €1.5M, hired 14 across Germany/Hungary/Russia, reached €1M in sales six months ahead of plan. Sold to strategic competitor in 2018.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-company">LUIS+ Group of Companies · 2004 – 2013</p>
        <p class="resume-role">Software Developer → Enterprise Account Executive</p>
        <p>Promoted from developer to enterprise sales; managed 100+ accounts with three direct reports. Led CRM/infrastructure migrations bridging business and engineering teams.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Education</h2>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-company">NYU Stern School of Business</p>
        <p class="resume-role">Executive MBA</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resume-entry">
        <p class="resume-company">Moscow Power Engineering Institute</p>
        <p class="resume-role">MS & BS, Electrical Engineering</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Skills</h2>
      <p>
        Product strategy · Growth · AI product management · Data governance · SQL ·
        Roadmapping · Stakeholder management · Experimentation · Platform thinking · Internal tooling
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .resume-content h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .resume-entry {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .resume-company {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .resume-role {
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      color: #4b5563;
      margin: 0.125rem 0 0.75rem 0;
    }
    .resume-entry ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .resume-entry ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .resume-entry > p:not(.resume-company):not(.resume-role) {
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .resume-content > p {
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
  </style>
</Base>
